# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CSE INTEL BRIEF — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your credentials.
# NEVER commit .env to git (it's in .gitignore).
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── REQUIRED: Anthropic Claude API ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# The pipeline uses Claude Opus 4.6 for analytical quality.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── OPTIONAL: Email Ingestion (CFR Daily Brief) ───────────────────────────────
# Gmail users: Create an App Password at https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# Then create a label "CFR-Daily" and set a filter to route CFR emails there.
CSE_EMAIL_USER=your@gmail.com
CSE_EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password

# ── OPTIONAL: Kpler API (Vessel Traffic / Energy Data) ───────────────────────
# Contact Kpler for API access: https://www.kpler.com/
# Leave blank to use blog scraping fallback for energy data.
KPLER_API_KEY=
